name: Screaming Man - Big-Headed Man Series - 8 x 10 print - by Shannon Kish
description:
This is a print of a larger pencil drawing entitled Screaming Man that I drew for my “Big-Headed Man” Series (this is actually the very first in the series—the impetus of all my big-headed men). This is an 8×10 print professionally printed on matte-finish photo paper…perfect for framing!

	Other sizes also available…just ask!

	Check out my other big-headed man prints as well!

	Thanks for looking!

name: Stoic Print - Big-Headed Man Series - By Shannon Kish
description:
Another print from my Big-Headed Man Series – this guy is Stoic. He’s a bit daunting at first, but he’ll grow on you. There’s a lot going on in those eyes. The original was drawn in pencil. I did pull this into Photoshop so I could play with the background a bit…so just that part of it is digital.

	This is an 8×10 print professionally printed on matte-finish photo paper…perfect for framing!

	Other sizes also available…just ask!

	Check out my other big-headed man prints as well!

name: Say Ahh... - 8x10 print - Big-Headed Man Series - Original Artwork by Shannon Kish
description:
This is my latest big-headed man. The original piece is quite large and is only the head. I digitally added some of my fractal art as a background for this guy. This is an 8×10 print professionally printed on matte photo paper. This print is also available in other sizes. Just ask!

	Thanks for looking!
